{"tid":912987,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【《(一個男人)一個女人和浴室》出MV】謝安琪除淨黑Bra 同古天樂喺浴室咀嘴","createTime":"2018-11-23T05:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T10:09:19.000Z","uid":22609,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe1ba078b8d44cbf688a6994ac5121020bd4215","tid":912987,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:32:10.000Z","msg":"《(一個男人)一個女人和浴室》出MV<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y0OQ6b38Pl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY0OQ6b38Pl0&d=2sUyXUM%2F3Pgi9fbUHNJmlRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=f7b7c80f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y0OQ6b38Pl0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542894449_6b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542894449_6b31.jpg&h=eaad8c4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542894449_c37b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542894449_c37b.jpg&h=33d7b574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542894449_fd35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542894449_fd35.jpg&h=1b472fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542894451_0129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542894451_0129.jpg&h=53a946a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542894451_02bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542894451_02bc.jpg&h=0e2a53d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542894451_c305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542894451_c305.jpg&h=cf591079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542894891_faa2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542894891_faa2.jpg&h=03038eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古天樂破天荒為麥浚龍同謝安琪嘅年度音樂企劃再踏樂壇，，早前古仔同謝安琪，就為兩人合唱新歌《（一個男人）一個女人和浴室》拍MV。<br />\n<br />\nMV講述謝安琪飾演嘅浦銘心同飾演佢第二任丈夫藍定凌嘅古天樂，喺浴室入面相處嘅默契，謝安琪喺MV入面激罕大膽演出，上身除淨黑Bra，再同古天樂咀嘴。拍攝嗰陣，佢哋都投入咗浦銘心同藍定凌嘅角色，所以大家都無尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n事後，謝安琪同古天樂都話兩個人相處，溝通係非常重要。已經係幸福人妻嘅謝安琪話：「兩個人一齊耐咗，一個動作已經知對方要乜。相處係需要時間，一齊耐咗自然有獨特嘅相處模式。假如兩個人都認定咗對方係另一半，有冇一紙約誓都唔再重要。」<br />\n<br />\n古天樂就分享佢父母嘅默契：「默契唔係一刻嘅事，我喺屋企見到爸爸同媽媽睇電視，大家會好有默契咁轉台，一句嘢都唔駛講。」佢仲話現實生活中嘅自己，都唔太重視一紙婚書：「感情係兩個人嘅事，有冇婚書唔太重要。我鍾意盡在不言中嘅安靜，如果兩個人都多嘢講，要喺同一個空間揾話題有時都幾攰，不如俾多啲時間關心同了解對方。」<br />\n<br />\n至於為MV擔任導演嘅麥浚龍，佢話因為拍電影《風林火山》識左古天樂，覺得佢嘅領悟力好高：「首歌出街嘅version，其實就係我想古仔咁唱，同佢以往嘅唱法好唔同，佢係飾演緊一個唔擅於唱歌、但默默配合緊太太嘅唱法。其實佢唱嗰陣感情好豐富，反而係我要㩒住佢，要佢做返藍定凌呢個角色。呢首合唱歌，我覺得好好，我好想多謝古天樂。」<br />\n<br />\n精選娛聞，喺晒《娛果》<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181123/58946573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F58946573&d=2sUyXUM%2F3Pgi9fbUHNJmlRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=fef18057\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F58946573&h=f44ac1a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181123/58946573</a>"},{"pid":"9ad90e9b364d326f739d425f294b564c303cf66d","tid":912987,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0d5df81df1dede81ccbab775ed2b6f67b23e9e","tid":912987,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j6yT5tM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj6yT5tM.jpg&h=4c41cac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Bh9DON.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Bh9DON.jpg&h=0c6f4b86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bDJdk17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbDJdk17.jpg&h=e025cf38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bU29DPV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbU29DPV.jpg&h=f1d7bad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBr6F3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBr6F3g.jpg&h=cc5ad4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFzDw9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFzDw9W.jpg&h=d9624113&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3789a944168cb19187b09cc2ead11c98d64b15f","tid":912987,"uid":69568,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:41:23.000Z","msg":"暗到乜7都睇5到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e1909aa5c9798162513eeb460d87efb18a1164","tid":912987,"uid":25653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"執bra執底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkg